# Depend on the various component packages, so they get built before the
# python stuff below.
use   DecayTreeTupleReco        v*    Phys
use   DecayTreeTupleDalitz      v*    Phys
use   DecayTreeTupleJets        v*    Phys
use   DecayTreeTupleMC          v*    Phys
